channel.title: VPS Questions
channel.description:
Just bought a Windows Vps under the Business Plan at www.vpsland.com
Atm, I havent done anything but buy the vps, some people say I must go to
search>run>MSTC
But when I type in user (People said Administrator) and pass (vpsland.com pass) it didnt work... Is there something I had to do, like tell them my current server ip?
